  
<h2>Minecraft server</h2>
<div id="minecraft_server_start" class="modal hide fade in" style="display: none; ">
    <div class="modal-header">
        <a class="close" data-dismiss="modal">×</a>
        <h3>Arrancar el servidor de minecraft</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
        <!--<h4>Arrancar el servidor de minecraft</h4>-->
        <p>Estas seguro que deseas arrancar el servidor de minecraft?</p>             
    </div>
    <div class="modal-footer">
        <a class="btn btn-success" href="{{ path('minecraft_server_start')}}">Start</a>
        <a href="#" class="btn" data-dismiss="modal">Close</a>
    </div>
</div>
<a data-toggle="modal" href="#minecraft_server_start" class="btn btn-success">Start</a>


<div id="minecraft_server_stop" class="modal hide fade in" style="display: none; ">
    <div class="modal-header">
        <a class="close" data-dismiss="modal">×</a>
        <h3>Parar el servidor de minecraft</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
        <!--<h4>Parar el servidor de minecraft</h4>-->
        <p>Estas seguro que deseas parar el servidor de minecraft?</p>             
    </div>
    <div class="modal-footer">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="{{ path('minecraft_server_stop')}}">Stop</a>
        <a href="#" class="btn" data-dismiss="modal">Close</a>
    </div>
</div>
<a data-toggle="modal" href="#minecraft_server_stop" class="btn btn-primary">Stop</a>

<div id="minecraft_server_stop_force" class="modal hide fade in" style="display: none; ">
    <div class="modal-header">
        <a class="close" data-dismiss="modal">×</a>
        <h3>Forzar la parada del servidor de minecraft</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
        <!--<h4>Forzar la parada del servidor de minecraft</h4>-->
        <p>Estas seguro que deseas forzar la parada del servidor de minecraft?</p>             
    </div>
    <div class="modal-footer">
        <a class="btn btn-danger" href="{{ path('minecraft_server_stop_force')}}">Force stop</a>
        <a href="#" class="btn" data-dismiss="modal">Close</a>
    </div>
</div>
<a data-toggle="modal" href="#minecraft_server_stop_force" class="btn btn-danger">Force stop</a>


<style>
div.scroll{ width:100%;margin-bottom:2em;max-height:400px;overflow-y: auto; }
</style>


<h2>Completed Backups</h2>
<div class="scroll">
    <pre>{{backups}}</pre>
</div>

{% if backupstemp %}
    <h2>Running backups</h2>
    <div class="scroll">
        <pre>{{backupstemp}}</pre>
    </div>
{% endif %}

